SYNOPSIS
        varargs void subdomain_shout(string sRoomPrefix, string sArg, 
          status tNoWiz, object * oExclude)

DESCRIPTION
        Does a "shout" to the subdomain sRoomPrefix. The message sArg
        will be in seen in their shout color, unless overriden. If
        tNoWiz is 1, it won't show to immortals. oExclude is an array
        of objects you don't want to see the shout.
